{"id":13,"idInBook":233,"chapterId":11,"bookId":15,"arabic":"حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ كَثِيرٍ، قَالَ‏:‏ أَخْبَرَنَا سُفْيَانُ، عَنْ أَبِي مَالِكٍ الأَشْجَعِيِّ، عَنْ رِبْعِيٍّ، عَنْ حُذَيْفَةَ قَالَ‏:‏ قَالَ نَبِيُّكُمْ صلى الله عليه وسلم‏:‏ كُلُّ مَعْرُوفٍ صَدَقَةٌ‏.‏","english":{"narrator":"","text":"Same as 231, but from Hudhayfa."},"hadithNumber":233,"hadithId":13,"reference":"11:13","meta":{"id":"aladab_almufrad","length":1326,"totalChapters":57,"arabic":{"title":"الأدب المفرد","author":"الإمام محمد بن إسماعيل البخاري"},"english":{"title":"Al-Adab Al-Mufrad","author":"Imam Muhammad ibn Ismail al-Bukhari"}},"chapter":{"id":11,"bookId":15,"arabic":"كتاب الْمَعْرُوفِ","english":"Good Conduct","startHadith":221,"endHadith":237,"totalHadiths":17},"version":{"name":"aladab_almufrad","title":"Al-Adab Al-Mufrad","chapters":57}}